Package: cyclinbayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian MCMC Methods for Cyclic and Acyclic Causal Graphs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Robert", "Lee", email = "robertdylee@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for Bayesian MCMC estimation of the structure of cyclic and
    acyclic causal graphs. Includes a Bayesian LiNGAM method BayesSCLingam for DAGs and a cyclic
    sampler BCD with priors adapted for feedback loops.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    igraph,
    HDInterval,
    ggplot2
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), roxygen2, SID
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
ByteCompile: true
SystemRequirements: C++17
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/roblee01/cyclinbayes
BugReports: https://github.com/roblee01/cyclinbayes/issues
